  "original_title": "LIOC \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "LIOC requests more gas stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Power and Energy says that the Ceylon Indian Oil Company has requested to increase the number of its petrol stations or to provide them with several Cipotco petrol stations.",
        "He stated this at a media briefing held in Colombo today. It is possible to give permission for that, but instead of giving dollars from the Central Bank for importing fuel, they have been asked to consider whether there is a way to buy oil through the Indian Oil Company, the Minister said."
      ],
